We could also return early with something like:

```tsx
  if (!connectedAddress) {
    return (
      <div className="bg-base-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">Connect your wallet to view your collected flags.</div>
    );
  }
```

For the target chain...Instead of:

```ts
// If you want to deploy to optimism:
// 1. import { optimism } from "viem/chains";
// 2. set TARGET_CHAIN = optimism;
```

Could we just import `import * as chains from "viem/chains";` as in scaffold.config?

So we can do

```ts
const TARGET_CHAIN = chains.optimism;
```
